228
00:16:52,604 --> 00:16:53,689
Atau untuk makan.

229
00:16:54,565 --> 00:16:55,899
Astaga. Ayo.

230
00:16:59,736 --> 00:17:03,282
Omong-omong, tulisannya "Han Ji-pyeong".
Siapa itu?

231
00:17:03,365 --> 00:17:04,741
- Itu kau?
- Ya.

232
00:17:06,660 --> 00:17:08,495
Anak muda sepertimu punya bakat begini?

233
00:17:08,579 --> 00:17:11,498
Berapa ini? Satu, dua, tiga…

234
00:17:11,582 --> 00:17:14,459
Seratus juta won?
Hadiah uang seratus juta won?

235
00:17:14,543 --> 00:17:16,712
Kau bisa bayar sewa rumah per tahun.

236
00:17:16,795 --> 00:17:18,380
- Bisa beli…
- Itu uang dunia maya.

237
00:17:18,463 --> 00:17:19,590
Uang dunia maya?

238
00:17:19,673 --> 00:17:21,174
UANG DUNIA MAYA

239
00:17:21,258 --> 00:17:22,593
Menyebalkan. Yang benar saja.

240
00:17:24,469 --> 00:17:25,304
Kalau begitu,

241
00:17:25,804 --> 00:17:29,182
cobalah berinvestasi sungguhan
alih-alih simulasi begini.

242
00:17:29,266 --> 00:17:32,519
Kau pasti bisa dapat uang sungguhan
dengan kemampuan begini.

243
00:17:33,604 --> 00:17:35,606
Aku belum 19 tahun.
Tak bisa buka rekening.

244
00:17:36,481 --> 00:17:38,692
Kenapa tak bisa? Anakku pun bisa.

245
00:17:38,775 --> 00:17:40,652
- Dengan orang tua…
- Aku tak punya orang tua.

246
00:17:41,486 --> 00:17:42,654
Benar. Maafkan aku.

247
00:17:44,197 --> 00:17:45,657
- Aku pergi dulu.
- Baik.

248
00:17:46,575 --> 00:17:47,409
Semangat!

249
